messages.message: Very strange :thinking_face: let me check and come back

Just to understand what I’m seeing @Anil are these full runs of compiled Build projects? Looking through my notes and catching up with the team, it seems the latency comes from the following:
• “Sometimes it takes 15+ minutes to upload documents into Converse; we tested this on documents of 20-140 pages”
• “It additionally previously took more than this when we asked a question at Converse; we found the latency to be better in Build but they come with different answers”
